The '''Spice Blades''' were a small elite force of [[Sevari]] serving under [[Spice lord|Spice Lord]] [[Cassius Nolath Rha]]. They were specially trained in [[Vibroblade/Legends|vibroblade]] and [[flashrifle]] combat and had a tendency to shoot first and ask questions later. They wore black and blood-red tunics, trousers and boots, and distinctive respirators pumping humidified [[Carsunum/Legends|black spice]] into their lungs, which made them totally loyal to their master.

